---
type ReadingBlock = {
  label?: string;
  original: string;
  translation?: string;
  note?: string;
  focus?: boolean;
};

interface Props {
  blocks: ReadingBlock[];
  extract: string | null;
}

const { blocks, extract } = Astro.props;
const hasCuratedBlocks = blocks.length > 0;
---

<section class="reading-section stack">
  <div class="reading-section__header">
    <h2>编者说明</h2>
    <p class="muted">这部分保留站内整理说明，帮助你判断这份资料该如何进入主稿、笔记和后续归档链路。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="reading-editorial">
    <slot name="editorial" />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="reading-section stack">
  <div class="reading-section__header">
    <h2>正文阅读</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      参考资料整理完成后，会在这里按段展示原文、对照翻译和编者备注。
      <span class="reading-focus">视频重点</span>
      会标出和视频主稿直接相关的段落。
    </p>
  </div>

  {
    hasCuratedBlocks ? (
      <div class="reading-stack">
        {blocks.map((block) => (
          <article class="reading-block">
            <div class="reading-block__head">
              <h3>{block.label ?? "正文段落"}</h3>
              {block.focus && <span class="reading-focus">视频重点</span>}
            </div>

            <div class="reading-original">
              <strong>原文</strong>
              <p>{block.original}</p>
            </div>

            {block.translation && (
              <div class="reading-translation">
                <strong>对照翻译</strong>
                <p>{block.translation}</p>
              </div>
            )}

            {block.note && <p class="reading-note">编者备注：{block.note}</p>}
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    ) : (
      <div class="reading-empty">
        <p>
          当前这份资料还没有整理成可逐段引用的正文阅读块。为了先保证站内可读和可引用，下面会先展示归档文本摘录；
          等后续补齐全文整理后，这里会自动切换成原文与对照翻译的阅读视图。
        </p>
      </div>
    )
  }
</section>

{
  extract && (
    <section class="reading-section text-extract stack">
      <div class="reading-section__header">
        <h2>站内摘录</h2>
        <p class="muted">这是从站内归档文件提取出的文字内容，适合先浏览、先定位，再逐步补成完整正文。</p>
      </div>
      <pre>{extract}</pre>
    </section>
  )
}
